{"tid":2220094,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"急症室醫生，你問我答（2）","createTime":"2020-09-27T11:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T12:32:36.000Z","uid":179902,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"1b545c85618e24954c34ca4a9a20ee35c89f4838","tid":2220094,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:21:28.000Z","msg":"估唔到要開2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知道呢度有好多老鬼，如果有得罪，多多包涵<br />\n上個post覆唔曬嘅絲打巴打，講聲唔好意思先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1634f116db4f345ed0546172e6c032b674d7583c","tid":2220094,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:22:19.000Z","msg":"肚痾可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痾水多氣"},{"pid":"61830c3dd4b5bb0fd220e268346e2c7c83605ecf","tid":2220094,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:24:38.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">見字開始手動呼吸</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd814681ccf0b0f0d0ca0a99dc1a06f67b37cee8","tid":2220094,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1634f116db4f345ed0546172e6c032b674d7583c","tid":2220094,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:22:19.000Z","msg":"肚痾可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痾水多氣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:26:16.000Z","msg":"如果係急性腸胃炎，休息多啲補充返電解質水分，自然就會好<br />\n如果係長期肚瀉就要搵下原因喇～睇下關唔關食過啲咩事，例如lactose intolerance飲完奶類就會肚瀉"},{"pid":"ce1b5299fe9e40f22fde621789cd28263c6954ac","tid":2220094,"uid":346806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:26:25.000Z","msg":"鍾意哆啦a夢嗎"},{"pid":"875b3a014f77fd49613e944b7ea2829e77705659","tid":2220094,"uid":194281,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:27:28.000Z","msg":"#1<br />\n腸蛋菜一丁麵<br />\n&bull;<br />\n2 年前<br />\n想問各位Ching，如果有眼科問題（之前試過kerato-conjunctivitis）想睇眼科，之前未睇過公立醫院眼科，應該直接去醫院眼科門診搵醫生，定要去普通科睇左普通科醫生，再等轉介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b0f068138d85e8b08fb977a33710ebd602c234","tid":2220094,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:27:46.000Z","msg":"#1<br />\n腸蛋菜一丁麵<br />\n&bull;<br />\n2 年前<br />\n想問各位Ching，如果有眼科問題（之前試過kerato-conjunctivitis）想睇眼科，之前未睇過公立醫院眼科，應該直接去醫院眼科門診搵醫生，定要去普通科睇左普通科醫生，再等轉介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19263eda171a249607af2cef955b8b0c3d803e86","tid":2220094,"uid":132554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:30:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hi. 胃好唔舒服 成日好漲 成日好多氣「Erh」出嚟<br />\n食過兩款成藥都無用 巳經Keep住兩三個禮拜 呢啲case係咪都可以睇急症？ 你係咪淨係開胃餅<blockquote>急症最多咪幫你按下個胃睇<br />\n再多啲好人嘅照張xray<br />\n跟住就refer番專科架啦</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689ef09792ff884bffa735d971e711c8fdb8bf8a","tid":2220094,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"60b0f068138d85e8b08fb977a33710ebd602c234","tid":2220094,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:27:46.000Z","msg":"#1<br />\n腸蛋菜一丁麵<br />\n&bull;<br />\n2 年前<br />\n想問各位Ching，如果有眼科問題（之前試過kerato-conjunctivitis）想睇眼科，之前未睇過公立醫院眼科，應該直接去醫院眼科門診搵醫生，定要去普通科睇左普通科醫生，再等轉介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:30:19.000Z","msg":"我而家知答案了<br />\n係要轉介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />公立專科無得直接睇"},{"pid":"1ffd146a7a6ac37951af5e954614cc7c5eed76a4","tid":2220094,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19263eda171a249607af2cef955b8b0c3d803e86","tid":2220094,"uid":132554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:30:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hi. 胃好唔舒服 成日好漲 成日好多氣「Erh」出嚟<br />\n食過兩款成藥都無用 巳經Keep住兩三個禮拜 呢啲case係咪都可以睇急症？ 你係咪淨係開胃餅<blockquote>急症最多咪幫你按下個胃睇<br />\n再多啲好人嘅照張xray<br />\n跟住就refer番專科架啦</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:33:34.000Z","msg":"xray都係簡單睇下骨、心肺大致有無問題<br />\n如果胃唔舒服黎急症都係開藥返屋企+/- 轉介居多，建議可以先去普通科/急症 搵醫生望下，再試其他藥<br />\n<br />\nbtw記得帶埋你有食過個兩隻成藥去睇醫生"},{"pid":"e31fcd6c74a2007a50688c600750beef6827a82f","tid":2220094,"uid":105592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:37:42.000Z","msg":"冇野問 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 醫生巴打，工作時要小心，大家都要保重身體~~"},{"pid":"721c2e9a9e3df3898e43766f653727a7b78936d5","tid":2220094,"uid":180105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:38:42.000Z","msg":"醫生係咪通常同返醫生一齊？<br />\n<br />\n食好多女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3089505c40b72584ac88840652718f0a0e6a4ac","tid":2220094,"uid":262327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:39:26.000Z","msg":"成日都頸渴<br />\n但得2X歲 會唔會真係糖尿？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9719b72abcfb62619411b763bbcb1def070bdd","tid":2220094,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e31fcd6c74a2007a50688c600750beef6827a82f","tid":2220094,"uid":105592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:37:42.000Z","msg":"冇野問 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 醫生巴打，工作時要小心，大家都要保重身體~~"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:41:27.000Z","msg":"多謝關心Ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家咁話"},{"pid":"28cca5bb942b95939e9d952e6ca16f6de56ef8f2","tid":2220094,"uid":17990