e":0,"quote":{"pid":"19263eda171a249607af2cef955b8b0c3d803e86","tid":2220094,"uid":132554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:30:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hi. 胃好唔舒服 成日好漲 成日好多氣「Erh」出嚟<br />\n食過兩款成藥都無用 巳經Keep住兩三個禮拜 呢啲case係咪都可以睇急症？ 你係咪淨係開胃餅<blockquote>急症最多咪幫你按下個胃睇<br />\n再多啲好人嘅照張xray<br />\n跟住就refer番專科架啦</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:33:34.000Z","msg":"xray都係簡單睇下骨、心肺大致有無問題<br />\n如果胃唔舒服黎急症都係開藥返屋企+/- 轉介居多，建議可以先去普通科/急症 搵醫生望下，再試其他藥<br />\n<br />\nbtw記得帶埋你有食過個兩隻成藥去睇醫生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:56:39.000Z","msg":"消化不良都可以多胃氣<br />\n有時候胃氣藥物都要時間先可以有作用，可以試耐啲先<br />\n當然如果好擔心，私家胃鏡可能會係你想要嘅嘢"},{"pid":"c40436f7160e29150ca4a4ae286edf0950915369","tid":2220094,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a864456aceb79286c3b401764ce6e3ab8db707c","tid":2220094,"uid":236855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:48:05.000Z","msg":"再續<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問你地醫生點睇港怡醫院？講到話同港大medic合作，會唔會好啲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:57:11.000Z","msg":"唔熟，等其他行家解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e0081835d9ea5fe099d6397c7a50afd6ce9e63","tid":2220094,"uid":369854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:58:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e6b13ddd7e3590521a28ee015285a96b4e9535d","tid":2220094,"uid":179902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37017aac437ebfaa283cd419f8b4132be27b31c7","tid":2220094,"uid":35575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:50:07.000Z","msg":"專科有無限考幾多次<br />\n<br />\n考極唔pass會點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返shift訓唔到會點做   有d護士食安眠藥<br />\n<br />\n急診室有無話邊間好做/唔好做<br />\n<br />\nmedico legal 嘅麻煩會唔會比其他科高<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麻煩晒    師弟上   想入A&amp;E<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:03:11.000Z","msg":"sor 頭兩樣我都答你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔清楚丫<br />\n<br />\n我知有師姐返唔慣shift，休息唔到訓唔到覺，最後由急症科轉走左，如果返shift失眠都係幾大嘅問題黎<br />\n<br />\n邊間好做唔好做呢度唔方便講喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你問下你啲seniors啦<br />\n<br />\nmedico legal問題呢，只可以講急症科都幾高危，因為你miss左診斷而導致病人受害，係要孭飛。所以返工都幾大壓力（尤其你discharge home嗰啲）"},{"pid":"1f0995677a045cefa825b1505220dcdf8b795410","tid":2220094,"uid":87820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:08:07.000Z","msg":"岩岩做身體檢查，低膽固醇去到3.9。總膽固醇5.9<br />\n<br />\n肝酵素都偏高，alt:105 alk:100<br />\n<br />\n醫生話4個月後再驗。想問下呢一刻使唔使再進一步檢查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時飲汽水多。知錯了"},{"pid":"3f6e9902f3fdad91db21f3a7febe597ae22d417c","tid":2220094,"uid":236855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"432b24709873e21bc78006523047df92cdc941dd","tid":2220094,"uid":369854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97d9195cd8e47df93d6fd430338dc2a8f25dbbf6","tid":2220094,"uid":63390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a864456aceb79286c3b401764ce6e3ab8db707c","tid":2220094,"uid":236855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:48:05.000Z","msg":"再續<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問你地醫生點睇港怡醫院？講到話同港大medic合作，會唔會好啲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:49:04.000Z","msg":"港怡<img src