79a93fdedf8ce7bf87ea7ceb828aa632a402bb","tid":2220094,"uid":358248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T13:08:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25c1ad82b73f2130cd19bedf253b5258a66708f6","tid":2220094,"uid":52051,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T13:15:49.000Z","msg":"想問如果睇急症嗰時唔知位醫生叫乜名？過咗十年仲可唔可以搵返佢係邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年我爆肺加肺膜血管出血(好似係咁講)，白車入咗急症室，初時我仲OK，護士見我好似無乜野分流咗我去cat 2定3，然後將我推埋一二邊等，但過咗一陣我已經無咗九成知覺，只係隱約聽到有個護士發現我，然後好快有個男醫生同我講幾句同唔同意，就即場做手術。<br />\n事後好返過咗半年到，個肺唔舒服怕又爆肺，去咗同一間醫院睇急症，個位醫生話好彩無事，因為上次個醫生已經無做呢度，呢隻手術得佢會做/識做(好似係咁講)。<br />\n一直好想多謝佢，但係當時幾次都無意識問返位醫生叫乜名。"},{"pid":"8fdcf2b647d4913b1ea5b95a3a6a65582005827d","tid":2220094,"uid":223838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b545c85618e24954c34ca4a9a20ee35c89f4838","tid":2220094,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:21:28.000Z","msg":"估唔到要開2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知道呢度有好多老鬼，如果有得罪，多多包涵<br />\n上個post覆唔曬嘅絲打巴打，講聲唔好意思先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8903e85895abec85b5e959dfb0fc559897542587","tid":2220094,"uid":132525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T16:47:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb1a3a37d952e230117511d91b2a3cca217c07a7","tid":2220094,"uid":22600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T16:57:32.000Z","msg":"近排有親人過左身 本身佢血壓都開始降緊 直到有一刻部機開始響紅燈 見到有一個數字跌到0 但中間都會有一兩下 突發跳返上2x 10秒左右 有一兩下仲上返120 但之後都係去返0<br />\n想問下係咩事"},{"pid":"2236ae79614809c8c2fdf72ebb20942c7dbb87f5","tid":2220094,"uid":188586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T17:01:47.000Z","msg":"返工係咪會忙到無時間睇電話？"},{"pid":"34202710934b9d5c23b9ffa7c54e2c1a30720149","tid":2220094,"uid":119807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T17:05:47.000Z","msg":"想問到底點去決定邊個睇醫生先，試過一次拎私家診所醫生紙去急症室，分流係次緊急但唔知點解15分鐘入得去見醫生，俾人推埋入手術室都係唔夠三個鐘嘅事<br />\n<br />\n同埋有一次試過血壓得5x/1x，再量直頭量唔到，我係唔係就死得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b468599c7f66c8331593920ce5d25ff8c0c869","tid":2220094,"uid":31205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T17:20:05.000Z","msg":"想投訴醫生失德係咪要搵醫委會"},{"pid":"dda68b79572e557fc96c68bb8ab766173c0b0c4b","tid":2220094,"uid":230197,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd814681ccf0b0f0d0ca0a99dc1a06f67b37cee8","tid":2220094,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1634f116db4f345ed0546172e6c032b674d7583c","tid":2220094,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:22:19.000Z","msg":"肚痾可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痾水多氣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:26:16.000Z","msg":"如果係急性腸胃炎，休息多啲補充返電解質水分，自然就會好<br />\n如果係長期肚瀉就要搵下原因喇～睇下關唔關食過啲咩事，例如lactose intolerance飲完奶類就會肚瀉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T17:21:22.000Z","msg":"Diarrhea  既Ddx 你會諗？！"},{"pid":"b19cb1ae5e477939551d17ef0a144b307940938f","tid":2220094,"uid":120836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T17:25:48.000Z","msg":"我間唔時會突然好肚痛，肚痾個隻痛，愈黎愈痛跟住開始暈，我試過幾次暈到無知覺成個人跌落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但一痾到出黎就即刻開始慢慢有返知覺，跟住一路痾一路成個人出汗成身濕晒，面青口唇白咁，痾/嘔到出黎就會慢慢無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一年總有幾次會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其黎m頭一兩日<br />\n請問點解會咁？有無解決辦法？"},{"pid":"9b735e43a2f866b81f76333629eeba90b2737a84","tid":2220094,"uid":251805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b545c85618e24954c34ca4a9a20ee35c89f4838","tid":2220094,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:21:28.000Z","msg":"估唔到要開2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知道呢度有好多老鬼，如果有得罪，多多包涵<br />\n上個post覆唔曬嘅絲打巴打，講聲唔好意思先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T17:25:51.000Z","msg":"32歲有高血壓，肥人， 上壓：157 下壓：117 去到幾多應該食藥？"},{"pid":"64dcd82018923b90e52b3f75d8808a619bf7292e","tid":2220094,"uid":202872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28cca5bb942b95939e9d952e6ca16f6de56ef8f2","tid":2220094,"uid":179902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3089505c40b72584ac88840652718f0a0e6a4ac","tid":2220094,"uid":262327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:39:26.000Z","msg":"成日都頸渴<br />\n但得2X歲 會唔會真係糖尿？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:43:55.000Z","msg":"糖尿病有所謂三高一低：飲水多、食嘢多、屙尿多、體重減輕<br />\n如果中曬就去驗下血糖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過有時飲食太鹹都會成日頸渴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T17:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d235d78f52e98bf0824bc10ffe951318271877","tid":2220094,"uid":202872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"34202710934b9d5c23b9ffa7c54e2c1a30720149","tid":2220094,"uid":119807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T17:05:47.000Z","msg":"想問到底點去決定邊個睇醫生先，試過一次拎私家診所醫生紙去急症室，分流係次緊急但唔知點解15分鐘入得去見醫生，俾人推埋入手術室都係唔夠三個鐘嘅事<br />\n<br />\n同埋有一次試過血壓得5x/1x，再量直頭量唔到，我係唔係就死得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T17:31:37.000Z","msg":"邊個就快頂唔順咪邊個睇先<br />\n應該係睇你咩事同生命跡象<br />\n<br />\n利申 9up"},{"pid":"8165c0ce572af9528765b95ebb7c1d52251b705b","tid":2220094,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T17:33:43.000Z","msg":"DDA box 入面有咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e593388a9fa